dict.string: Toggle WiFi shell script no AppleScript

#!/usr/bin/env bash # source Keyboard Maestro forum: https://forum.keyboardmaestro.com/t/switching-wifi-on-and-off/803
device=$(networksetup -listallhardwareports | grep -E '(Wi-Fi|AirPort)' -A 1 | grep -o en.) [[ "$(networksetup -getairportpower $device)" == *On ]] && v=off || v=on networksetup -setairportpower $device $v
